leadmill-sheffield-venue-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/the-leadmill-sheffield-venue-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/the-leadmill-sheffield-venue-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>谢菲尔德利德米尔工厂的经营者表示，在建筑物所有者获得新的影子许可证后，他们“仍然反抗”关闭。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/sheffield-leadmill-arctic-monkeys-closes-we-all-lose-something-3196736">如果谢菲尔德的 Leadmill——帮助击败北极猴子的场地——消失了，我们都会失去一些东西</a></strong></li></ul><p>去年三月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/artists-voice-support-for-sheffields-the-leadmill-as-iconic-venue-announces-eviction-and-closure-3195218">The Leadmill 宣布因房东发出驱逐通知而面临关闭威胁</a>。这一消息引发了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/artists-voice-support-for-sheffields-the-leadmill-as-iconic-venue-announces-eviction-and-closure-3195218">音乐界人士和演出观众的强烈抗议</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hearing-begins-to-determine-future-the-leadmill-huge-rally-support-gathers-sheffield-3499854">随后于周一（9 月 18 日）开始了一场许可听证会</a>，以确定该场地的未来， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sheffield-leadmill-operators-and-new-building-owners-come-to-blows-over-eviction-during-licence-hearing-3501892">Leadmill 老板菲尔·米尔斯 (Phil Mills) 的代理律师指责新老板多米尼克·马登 (Dominic Madden) “傲慢”</a> 。</p><p>该建筑的业主 Electric Group 于 2017 年购买了该场地的永久业权，此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sheffield-leadmill-bosses-claim-landlords-are-exterminating-them-after-they-denied-plans-to-close-venue-3195917">曾告诉音乐迷，他们无意在 2023 年当前占用者的租约结束时关闭该场地</a>。 Electric Group 首席执行官兼联合创始人 Madden 当时在 Twitter 上写道：“管理层可能会发生变化，但歌曲不会变。” </p><div class="Markup__ParagraphWrapper-sc-13q6ywe-0 Markup__ParagraphWrapperInews-sc-13q6ywe-1 jvvDEQ gqFwNZ markup "><div class="Markup__ParagraphWrapper-sc-13q6ywe-0 Markup__ParagraphWrapperInews-sc-13q6ywe-1 hqSJcf gqFwNZ markup "><p> Madden 的公司 MVL Properties 2017 Ltd 将 The Leadmill 从 Leadmill 路的场地驱逐后申请了影子许可证来运营谢菲尔德场馆，该俱乐部自 1980 年开业以来一直在该场地运营。现在，MVL 已获得谢菲尔德的许可申请市议会。</p></div></div><p>影子许可证可保护房东在租户搬出后继续在场地内经营有许可的场所的权利。</p><p>由米尔斯领导的场馆运营商 The Leadmill Ltd 表示，在做出决定后，该场馆的未来“远未结束”，并表示“正在考虑未来几天的下一步行动”。</p><p>他们在 Instagram 上写道：“谢菲尔德许可小组委员会今天决定向我们的房东授予影子许可证。</p><p> “然而，为 The Leadmill 及其员工的未来而战还远未结束，我们将在接下来的几天内考虑下一步的行动。所有预定的活动仍将按计划进行，在法律程序继续进行的同时，我们将继续在未来进一步安排活动。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CxfuwWxqLWZ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.6